snippet.title: Lunar 2: Eternal Blue Complete (PS1) Playthrough #1 (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Lunar Series: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPO56tlewLYRkluLYfceIt_gEeQDjajsV
Goofs. Hijinks. Shenanigans.
Please note that this is segmented and edited.
Like with the original Lunar, the game is balanced around you fighting the majority of encounters and these are included.

Notes
Some spicy dialogue this time around. Wish it would lay off on the immersion breaking references, though.
